	<h1>MBlo Help</h1>
	<h2> 
	  Join the MBlo family by clicking the Sign-Up button in Home page</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  Fill your details in the Sign-Up form and click on Create button</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  You will be sent an email  with a link to activate your account</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  Click on the activation link to get started with MBlo</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  <%= link_to image_tag("voila.svg", alt: "Voila", :width => 100, :height => 73, :class=>"center") %></br>You are now an MBlo member!</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  Navigate to Home page to add new posts</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  Visit Users-to-Follow page link (appears when you login) to follow people.</br>&#x21E9</br>
	  Once you follow some users, their posts will start appearing in your micropost feed.</br>&#x21E9</br>
  	  Navigate to Settings page in Accounts dropdown menu (appears when you login) to change your profile picture, password and more.</br>
	  </br>You can also request password resets by clicking Forgot-password link while trying to login.
  	</h2>
  	<h1><i>Happy Blogging!</i></h1>
